details.text: Director of the Foreign Intelligence Service (Oct 2016 - ). Member of the State Duma of the Federal Assembly (Oct 2016). Chairman of the State Duma of the Federal Assembly (Dec 2011 - Sep 2016). Member of State Council of the Russian Federation (reported 2014 - ). Chairman of the Parliamentary Assembly of the Union of Belarus and Russia (Apr 2012 - ). Chief of Staff of the Presidential Executive Office (May 2008 - Dec 2011). Member of the Security Council of the Russian Federation (reported 2016- ). Member of the Board of Directors (2004-2010) and Chairman of the Board of Directors of Sovcomflot (SOE) (2010-2011). Deputy Prime Minister and Chief of Staff of the RF Government (Feb 2007 - May 2008). Member of the Board of Directors, Deputy Chairman of the Board of Directors of Open Joint-Stock Company Rosneft (SOE) (2004-2009). Chief of Staff of the Government and Minister (Sep 2004 - Feb 2007). President of All-Russian Swimming Federation (Jan 2006 - ). Member of Edinaya Rossiya.
details.title: BIOGRAPHY

details.text: Apr 2015 - Verkhovna Rada of Ukraine adopted a Resolution on recommending to the National Security and Defence Council of Ukraine (NSDC) to impose sanctions against persons responsible for illegal imprisonment of Ukrainian officer, Verkhovna Rada deputy and member of Permanent Delegation to Parliamentary Assembly of Council of Europe Nadiya Savchenko. Sep 2015 - sanctioned (asset freeze, visa ban) for 1 year by the Ukrainian National Security and Defence Council (UANSDC) for activities that create real or potential threats to national interests, national security, sovereignty and territorial integrity, that facilitate terrorist activities in relation to the annexation of Crimea and aggression in Donbass. Sep 2016 - UANSDC sanctions extended for 1 year.
